        \dd{B} = \frac{(4\pi \times 10^{-7})(2)(2\hat{k} \times (-6\hat{i}))}{4\pi \times 6^3} = -1.11 \times 10^{-8} \hat{j}
        \]
        Thus, \(\dd{B} = 1.11 \times 10^{-8} \, \text{T}\) along the negative y-axis.

